


Exceptions:

`SessionException` error codes:

you should pass error number to `SessionException` once you throw it, don't pass a string message to `SessionException` as it will not worked and will not constructing the exception.

passing number other than the listed will make exception return string with explainations, avoid it please and implement your exception class inherited from `SessionException` instead.

you have the following error code options:

    SessionException::ERR_CODE_DATA_NOT_FOUND : this is used when you expect some fields in session and you can't find them

